WEBVTT

00:00:00.380 --> 00:00:02.793
Alam mo na siguro ang
horizontal centering ng text

00:00:02.818 --> 00:00:04.206
gamit ang text-align: center.

00:00:05.468 --> 00:00:07.468
Pero alam mo ba na puwede
mo na ring i-center ang

00:00:07.492 --> 00:00:09.619
buong paragraph vertically
gamit ang align-content?

00:00:10.865 --> 00:00:13.095
Siguruhin na naka-display:
block ang parent element.

00:00:14.118 --> 00:00:16.507
Kapag naka-set to center
ang align-content property,

00:00:16.809 --> 00:00:18.809
gigitna ang buong paragraph vertically

00:00:18.834 --> 00:00:20.834
basta may extra space
pa ang parent container.

00:00:22.291 --> 00:00:24.076
At hindi lang ito para sa mga text ha.

00:00:24.764 --> 00:00:26.764
Gumagana rin ito sa iba pang mga elements

00:00:26.788 --> 00:00:28.788
basta naka-display:
block ang parent container.

00:00:30.447 --> 00:00:31.915
Dahil bago ang feature na ito,

00:00:32.325 --> 00:00:34.325
gagana lang ito sa mga bagong browsers.

00:00:35.249 --> 00:00:37.523
Pero puwede mo na itong
gamitin dahil Baseline na ito.

00:00:38.132 --> 00:00:39.957
Siguruhin lang na usable pa rin ang

00:00:39.981 --> 00:00:41.981
layout mo kahit na hindi
ito vertically centered.